{"tid":871321,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟 西北兩新盤混戰 朗城滙弦海共收3000票 2018/10/22","createTime":"2018-10-22T00:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T02:40:54.000Z","uid":130169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2213fb442ad0175cd5ba8554e6af6149d8fb8a6","tid":871321,"uid":130169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】新界西北兩大新盤正面對撼，並同步加推，其中華懋元朗朗屏朗城滙加推216伙，令項目已公布價單之單位增至504伙、即佔全盤七成，樓盤至昨日暫收約2500張入票，超額4倍。另莊士中國（0298）屯門弦海加推100伙，以目前已公布175個單位價單、收約500票計，超額近兩倍。"},{"pid":"78aa8a508611760296afc3d7d757ed9c0c040945","tid":871321,"uid":130169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81151e486d4afc6ca81fbc5f287abeaba9111492","tid":871321,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"2500應該有2400係地產狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4e9e92aa2f36267ce2564a96c93db6443a323a","tid":871321,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04b1PW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04b1PW.gif&h=ccc4c9cf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}